661
00:30:34,350 --> 00:30:37,870
Also, I haven’t finished it yet.

662
00:30:40,200 --> 00:30:41,720
Yesterday, you said this morning.

663
00:30:41,720 --> 00:30:43,030
And this morning, you said tonight.

664
00:30:43,270 --> 00:30:44,870
