from a success to a failure.

677
00:31:21,160 --> 00:31:22,900
My daytime can only
belong to my patients.

678
00:31:24,400 --> 00:31:25,390
And that matter of yours

679
00:31:27,720 --> 00:31:29,070
will be dealt with at night.

