697
00:32:27,260 --> 00:32:28,240
Director Yan.

698
00:32:28,240 --> 00:32:29,270
You heard about that?

699
00:32:29,270 --> 00:32:30,390
I also heard

700
00:32:30,390 --> 00:32:31,510
that after you identified yourself,

701
00:32:31,510 --> 00:32:33,550
