00:32:45,750 --> 00:32:46,740
Actually,

708
00:32:46,920 --> 00:32:48,870
you trying to walk into
doctors’ daily life

709
00:32:49,030 --> 00:32:50,940
is a very good start.

710
00:32:51,790 --> 00:32:53,020
Mediation

711
00:32:53,020 --> 00:32:55,630
