784
00:35:18,110 --> 00:35:19,630
I just want to prove myself.

785
00:35:20,000 --> 00:35:20,630
But now,

786
00:35:20,630 --> 00:35:21,440
my loyal guests

787
00:35:21,440 --> 00:35:22,590
