800
00:35:43,320 --> 00:35:45,430
how he sounded and looked like.

801
00:35:46,320 --> 00:35:47,260
Get out.

802
00:35:47,510 --> 00:35:48,910
Could you stand that?

803
00:35:49,190 --> 00:35:51,660
